{"title":"Ubuntu 上安装 Hexo","slug":"2017/12/install-hexo-on-ubuntu","date":"2017-12-25T15:34:50.000Z","updated":"2020-05-12T08:18:10.204Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/2017/12/install-hexo-on-ubuntu.json","excerpt":null,"covers":null,"content":"<p>执行如下命令：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install                                   <span class=\"comment\">#Install dependencies</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save          <span class=\"comment\">#Install deploy</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>出现这个错误：-bash: hexo: command not found</p>\n<hr>\n<p>执行如下命令：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo npm install-g hexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>出现这个错误：/usr/bin/env: node: No such file or directory</p>\n<hr>\n<p>执行这个命令，最终解决。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo ln -s /usr/bin/nodejs /usr/bin/node</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","more":"<p>执行如下命令：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install                                   <span class=\"comment\">#Install dependencies</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save          <span class=\"comment\">#Install deploy</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>出现这个错误：-bash: hexo: command not found</p>\n<hr>\n<p>执行如下命令：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo npm install-g hexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>出现这个错误：/usr/bin/env: node: No such file or directory</p>\n<hr>\n<p>执行这个命令，最终解决。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo ln -s /usr/bin/nodejs /usr/bin/node</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","categories":[{"name":"Hexo","path":"api/categories/Hexo.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Hexo","path":"api/tags/Hexo.json"},{"name":"Blog","path":"api/tags/Blog.json"},{"name":"Ubuntu","path":"api/tags/Ubuntu.json"}]}